00:19:36.960 --> 00:19:38.799
Be careful, don't trust anyone too easily.

00:19:40.960 --> 00:19:42.519
Okay, I understand.

00:19:44.039 --> 00:19:46.839
Did you forget about me too?

00:19:47.200 --> 00:19:48.079
Of course not.

00:19:49.519 --> 00:19:50.880
Our time in college

00:19:51.599 --> 00:19:53.720
