00:20:29.160 --> 00:20:31.000
How much do you still remember about her?

00:20:36.039 --> 00:20:37.400
I just remember she had bad luck with people.

00:20:39.160 --> 00:20:39.880
And she's a bit wary of men.

00:20:45.519 --> 00:20:46.240
So she...

00:20:46.519 --> 00:20:47.359
I'm a bit tired.

00:20:49.359 --> 00:20:50.200
Let's talk tomorrow.

