Hello

00:21:47.440 --> 00:21:48.839
Xu Xin saw Xixi today.

00:22:38.920 --> 00:22:39.599
Do you remember?

00:22:40.920 --> 00:22:42.279
We're meeting Teacher Zhong today.

00:22:43.559 --> 00:22:44.599
Teacher Zhong.

00:22:47.039 --> 00:22:47.640
That's right.

00:22:48.960 --> 00:22:51.359
We haven't seen each other much since graduation.

00:22:55.480 --> 00:22:57.640
We arranged this a few days ago.

00:23:22.400 --> 00:23:22.920
Let's go.

00:23:41.279 --> 00:23:43.839
Lu Ming, Xu Xin, it's been a long time.

00:23:44.160 --> 00:23:45.960
Teacher Zhong, it's been a while.

00:23:46.880 --> 00:23:47.480
Come in.

00:24:04.160 --> 00:24:04.759
Xiaoya.

00:24:05.599 --> 00:24:06.799
My two students are here.

00:24:18.039 --> 00:24:20.640
Teacher Zhong, your home is beautiful.

00:24:21.720 --> 00:24:22.920
It's all thanks to Xiaoya.

00:24:23.839 --> 00:24:25.759
She designed everything here.

00:24:28.240 --> 00:24:29.720
Seeing you both so happy now,

00:24:30.119 --> 00:24:31.000
